ry thoughtful enemy placement to force you to engage with difficult enemies, instead of just running through. And then for some reason the devs remembered you can just spam the same enemy 50 times in a row across the map like it's Lost Izalith and call it a day. Or spam / strengthen enemies that are broken (Gaius, PCR, Leonine Misbegotten) instead of improving them. The beginning of the mod feels like it wants to be an excruciatingly hard yet still a bit fair, everything else feels more troll than anything, as if both parts were created by two people with different visions, who never spoke to each other, except to agree on the fact that they disagreed on what the mod should be.\n\nAnyways, congrats Aggy on beating this nightmare","author":{"type":"https://schema.org/Person","name":"@sylmir6620","url":"https://www.youtube.com/@sylmir6620","alternateName":"Sylmir"},"upvoteCount":1261}]}}},"frameworkUpdates":{"entityBatchUpdate":{"mutations":[{"entityKey":"EgpIRUFUU0VFS0VSIJICKAE%3D","type":"ENTITY_MUTATION_TYPE_REPLACE","payload":{"macroMarkersListEntity":{"key":"EgpIRUFUU0VFS0VSIJICKAE%3D","externalVideoId":"HZ9B7Gtdl8U","markersList":{"markerType":"MARKER_TYPE_HEATMAP","markers":[{"startMillis":"0","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.66948071879448079},{"startMillis":"126320","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.8979917552356218},{"startMillis":"252640","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.75610078680609916},{"startMillis":"378960","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.96509998300136646},{"startMillis":"505280","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.83329344681321182},{"startMillis":"631600","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.68894365593626739},{"startMillis":"757920","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.38924664163093492},{"startMillis":"884240","durationMillis":"126320","intensityScoreNormalized":0.47711427267345796},{"startMillis":"1010560